Tags:
  - Beauty-Peace=Beauty=The Universal Harmony
Commentary: This luminous pneumatic thread is the same as the 'Gale of the
  Spirit'; cf The Emerald Table of Hermes, 'The Wind carried it in its womb.'
---
Wind, verily, O Gautama, is that thread. By wind, verily. O Gautama, as by a
thread, this world and the other world and all things are tied together.
